title: Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5
text:
> Sports Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5 Toronto Blue Jays Jose Bautista, left, celebrates his three-run homer with teammates Ryan Goins, right, and Josh Donaldson (20) during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto. (Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
